snippet.title: Devious Dungeon - Google Play Trailer
snippet.description:
Devious Dungeon is a medieval action platformer by the guys behind Random Heroes and League of Evil. Fight your way through randomized dungeons locating the key to open the portal. Slay enemies, collect loot, earn experience, and level up! Only a true champion will be victorious!

Coming to Google Play July 31st

Check us out at http://www.ravenousgames.com
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/ravenousgames
Twitter: http://twitter.com/ravenousgames
